30-DAY DEMO TERMS
=================

- Self-hosted demo packages are licensed for **30 calendar days** on **one domain**
  per active BILOHASH ecosystem plan.
- After 30 days you must **purchase or renew** a subscription, remove the installation,
  or contact the author for extension.
- The public demo at https://bilohash.com/landing_builder/builder.php is for evaluation
  only — changes stay in the browser; no server persistence.

